      • processGroup

        protected void processGroup(List<gate.Annotation> group,
                gate.AnnotationSet consensusAS,
                gate.AnnotationSet disputeAS)
                     throws gate.creole.ExecutionException
        Process a single group of co-extensive annotations, and either create a consensus annotation if there is sufficient agreement, or copy them all to the dispute set if not.
        Parameters:
        group - the group of annotations to process, which will all have exactly the same span.
        consensusAS - consensus set
        disputeAS - disputed set
        Throws:
        gate.creole.ExecutionException
